{
  "stem": "21609.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were afraid, after the war, that some-- they-- they would capture them, for some reason, and do something to them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they-- they left me at a train station, in the city of Rowno, which is the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, we'll be right back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, 10, 15, 20 minutes later, nothing happened, and I was left alone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I decided-- it was at night-- I slept in the train station by myself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the next morning, I got up, and I was wandering around the city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The little town.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I sat down near a-- a house, and this couple took me in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Their names were the Achtenbaums.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were Jewish, and they took me in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I lived with them until I came here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the Russians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Russians came in, and-- and before we could do anything, they-- they made sure that we were clean and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I remember having to go through--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were the ones with us-- they were in the woods with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Evidently, they were running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were running for some reason, or being afraid of being captured as being Communist.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't under-- quite understand why.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- And they just-- just left me alone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, and took me in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they-- they had their-- they lived in an apartment, I guess it was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I lived with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from there, from Rowno, we went to France.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They decided we want-- right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They decided they weren't going to stay there, and they-- and we moved to France.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I lived in France from '45 to '48.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I remember the train ride.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was-- for a kid, I've never been on a train before.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
